net.sitecore.android.sdk.api.provider

Class ScItemsContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sitecore.android.sdk.api.provider.ScItemsContract

  • public class ScItemsContract
extends java.lang.Object
    Contract between ScItemsProvider and other applications. Contains supported URIs and data columns.

    Data tables:

    • ScItemsContract.Items stores downloaded items.
    • ScItemsContract.Fields contains fields of particular item.

    Supported Query URIs:

    • content://AUTHORITY/items returns all items.
    • content://AUTHORITY/items/{item_id} returns specific item.
    • content://AUTHORITY/fields returns all fields.

    Delete:

    • content://AUTHORITY/items delete all items.
    • content://AUTHORITY/fields delete all fields item.
